    "body" : "<p>Use <code>Thread.sleep(1000)</code>;</p>\n<p><code>1000</code> is the number of milliseconds that the program will pause.</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>try {\n  Thread.sleep(1000);\n} catch (InterruptedException e) {\n  Thread.currentThread().interrupt();\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
