      "body" : "Using <code>catch (InterruptedException e) { &#47;* empty *&#47; }</code> is <b>NOT</b> a sensible solution here. At the very least, you should provide some log information. For more information about the subject, see <a href=\"https://www.javaspecialists.eu/archive/Issue056.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">javaspecialists.eu/archive/Issue056.html</a>"
