    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 5833251,
      "reputation" : 451,
      "user_id" : 11949667,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/805b1f5877884fdc731483ba51dcabe4?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Hecanet",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/11949667/hecanet"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 35,
    "last_activity_date" : 1593332941,
    "last_edit_date" : 1593332941,
    "creation_date" : 1566278161,
    "answer_id" : 57567069,
    "question_id" : 24104313,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use this:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>public static void wait(int ms)\n{\n    try\n    {\n        Thread.sleep(ms);\n    }\n    catch(InterruptedException ex)\n    {\n        Thread.currentThread().interrupt();\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>and, then you can call this method anywhere like:</p>\n<pre><code>wait(1000);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
