  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/24104313/how-do-i-make-a-delay-in-java",
  "title" : "How do I make a delay in Java?",
  "body" : "<p>I am trying to do something in Java and I need something to wait / delay for an amount of seconds in a while loop.</p>\n<pre><code>while (true) {\n    if (i == 3) {\n        i = 0;\n    }\n\n    ceva[i].setSelected(true);\n\n    // I need to wait here\n\n    ceva[i].setSelected(false);\n\n    // I need to wait here\n\n    i++;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>I want to build a step sequencer.</p>\n<p>How do I make a delay in Java?</p>\n"
